From <a href="http://www.ne-mo.org/our-topics/collection-mobility/nemo-standard-loan-agreement.html">www.ne-mo.org/our-topics/collection-mobility/nemo-standard-loan-agreement.html</a>.<br><br>This form agreement has many alternatives - including seven different possibilities for liability.  The various alternatives each are stated as a separate section, making them seperately includable.  The alternatives are collected into a choice section, which means that they can also be selected among using the convention "Topic.Sec=Topic.Alt2.Sec".  